<p><ent>Bugle</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 5 ====
HEADWORD: Bugle
<hw>Bu"gle</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>bugle</ets>; cf. It.
<ets>bugola</ets>, L. <ets>bugillo</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A plant of the genus <gen>Ajuga</gen> of the Mint family, a native
of the Old World.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Yellow bugle</b></col>, <cd>the <spn>Ajuga
cham⟦ae⟧pitys</spn>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

